European Fund Grants Loan Guarantees to Unicredit in Romania

-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 
2011-12-13T09:20:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/european-fund-grants-loan-guarantees-to-unicredit-in-romania.html
The  European Investment Fund   signed
an agreement with  Unicredit SpA (UCG) ’s Romanian unit to offer 87.5
million euros ($116 million) in loan guarantees to small-and
medium-sized companies, according to an e-mailed statement.  The fund’s guarantees will allow Unicredit Tiriac Bank SA
to extend SME lending in  Romania  over the next two years, the
bank said in the statement. The European investment fund is a
unit of the  European Investment Bank .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  